
* chear *

Usage: chear <sky> all/swears/nothing

This sets what part of the conversation in the clones sky the clone will
display to you. "all" makes it show all that is being said and emoted , 
"swears" will make it just report swearing and "nothing" will force it to 
ignore everything.

See also: .clone, .destroy, .allclones, .myclones, .csay, .switch

